ors must contain number of signatures of electors cast in relevant electoral district at last presidential election. Establishes signature requirement for certificate of nomination made by individual electors following change in boundaries of electoral district. Removes vector control districts from definition of district for purposes of special district elections. Alters procedures for hearing on whether to impose civil penalty for failing to properly file campaign finance statements. Clarifies that certain campaign finance statements may be filed electronically. Revises statutes to make clear that county clerk or other filing officer is not required to provide secrecy envelope for ballot if Secretary of State has approved alternative procedure to ensure secrecy. Authorizes county clerk to begin tallying any ballot received upon receipt of ballot. Requires each sheet of recall petition to include city and state of residence of chief petitioner, rather than address of chief petitioner. Declares emergency, effective on passage.", "pending_committee_id": 0, "committee": [], "referrals": [{"date": "2021-01-19", "committee_id": 1850, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 82, "name": "Rules"}, {"date": "2021-06-08", "committee_id": 1835, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 81, "name": "Rules"}], "history": [{"date": "2021-01-11", "action": "Introduction and first reading. Referred to President's desk.", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 82, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2021-01-19", "action": "Referred to Rules.", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 82, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2021-03-09", "action": "Public Hearing held.", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 82, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2021-04-01", "action": "Work Session cancelled.", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 82, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2021-04-15", "action": "Work Session held.", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 82, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2021-05-03", "action": "Recommendation: Do pass with amendments. (Printed A-Eng.)", "chamber": 